    "en": {
      "title": "Firing in Ambalangoda: Two killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ambalangodai - Two people have died and two others have been seriously injured in a shooting that took place yesterday (21) evening at a restaurant in Thelduva, police said.",
        "It is reported that 4 people were on the upper floor of the guest house at the time of the shooting incident. This firing has been done using Re-56 rifle.",
        "This is the third shooting incident in Ambalangoda within a month. (a)"
      ],
